nodes.text: "No Sympathy" is a comic strip written by Martin Fisher, drawn by Bob Molesworth and edited by Gunther Nickel. The story was published in the fourteenth issue of the Star Wars Rebels Magazine series by Egmont UK Ltd, which was released on January 27, 2016.
According to Fisher, the story takes place between the Star Wars Rebels episodes "Wings of the Master" and "Blood Sisters."
